{"title":"Hexo搜索引擎收录","uid":"e0d737012fb60b73df4f5e8933a18018","slug":"Hexo搜索引擎","date":"2023-12-07T07:20:22.000Z","updated":"2023-12-09T01:03:59.079Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo搜索引擎.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"Hexo搜索引擎收录\"><a href=\"#Hexo搜索引擎收录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hexo搜索引擎收录\"></a>Hexo搜索引擎收录</h1><h2 id=\"百度×\"><a href=\"#百度×\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"百度×\"></a><del>百度</del>×</h2><ol>\n<li><p>我在提交百度搜索引擎时，验证网页时，只提供了文件验证和<code>html</code>验证</p>\n<p>没有<code>CNAME</code>验证方式，验证时频繁验证失败</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>即使更改验证文件，拒绝渲染也是无法通过，遂暂不提交</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ps：头条通过更改验证文件，即可以通过验证</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071421740.png\" alt=\"image-20231207142153661\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>通过检索的得知，文件验证显示<code>301</code>时，大概率<code>html</code>也是<code>error</code>，所以我就直接略过了</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"谷歌\"><a href=\"#谷歌\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"谷歌\"></a>谷歌</h2><ol>\n<li><p>进入<a href=\"https://www.google.com/webmasters/tools/\">谷歌站长平台</a>，登录账号后，会验证网站的所有权。</p>\n<p>此处选了CNAME验证方式</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>后续有引擎是采取的文件验证</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>ps：我是绑定了阿里云的域名，直接在域名解析添加记录就可以</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071343094.png\" alt=\"image-20231207134314068\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>安装 <code>hexo-generator-sitemap</code>插件：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install hexo-generator-sitemap --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>会在根目录下生成<code>public</code>文件夹</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>修改在根目录下的项目文件<code>_config.yml</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"># URL</span><br><span class=\"line\">url: https://cylin.cn   </span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"># url更改为在谷歌站长平台添加的域名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>部署网站</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo c</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo g -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>访问<code>你的首页/sitemap.xml</code>即可访问网站地图</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>将<code>你的首页/sitemap.xml</code>此网址链接提交到谷歌站长平台</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071352346.png\" alt=\"image-20231207135251208\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071428486.png\" alt=\"image-20231207142802303\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"必应\"><a href=\"#必应\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"必应\"></a>必应</h2><ol>\n<li><p>进入<a href=\"https://www.bing.com/webmaster/home/mysites\">必应站长平台</a>注册账号后登录</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>必应收录可以提供谷歌导入转移</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>转移完成后，如上提交.xml文件即可</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071424706.png\" alt=\"image-20231207142439550\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"360搜索\"><a href=\"#360搜索\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"360搜索\"></a>360搜索</h2><ol>\n<li><p>打开<a href=\"https://zhanzhang.so.com/sitetool/site_manage\">360站长平台</a>注册登录</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071435725.png\" alt=\"image-20231207143510541\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071438219.png\" alt=\"image-20231207143835104\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>txt文件验证失败，遂选择CNAME验证</p>\n<p>（合着到最后只有<code>头条</code>通过更改验证文件，拒绝渲染，才通过了文件验证）</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071442801.png\" alt=\"image-20231207144241713\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071445740.png\" alt=\"image-20231207144556629\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"头条\"><a href=\"#头条\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"头条\"></a>头条</h2><ol>\n<li><p>搜索头条站长平台，注册登录</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071450866.png\" alt=\"image-20231207145033756\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>此处选择文件验证，并如下修改验证文件</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>hexo发布网站的时候渲染了验证文件，导致无法辨认自己的验证文件</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071503890.png\" alt=\"image-20231207150331788\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071452631.png\" alt=\"image-20231207145217551\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>进行部署</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo c</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo g -d </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071504447.png\" alt=\"image-20231207150405249\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>提交.xml文件即可</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cyl-ly/picture/blogimage/202312071505835.png\" alt=\"image-20231207150511617\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","text":"Hexo搜索引擎收录百度× 我在提交百度搜索引擎时，验证网页时，只提供了文件验证和html验证 没有CNAME验证方式，验证时频繁验证失败 即使更改验证文件，拒...","permalink":"/post/Hexo搜索引擎","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":785,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Hexo%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E%E6%94%B6%E5%BD%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Hexo搜索引擎收录</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level